features: [Premium Quality Mterial] Durable PP material plastic envelope folder, The envelope folder size is 13.25 x 9.25 inches perfect for US letter/A4 size paper and other small items storage.
[Colorful Transparent Envelopes] 6 assorted colors: transparent blue, green, yellow, purple, pink and red. It’s easy to organize and distinguish your paper with a different color.

[Easy Storage] Our plastic pouch is portable to keep your items organized and help you sort the clutter, the envelopes bags can be used at school, home, work, office travel, and business trip. Outside mini label pocket helps classify and identify your document.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I have five older cats. Not all of them have medical conditions, but they do need yearly vaccinations and regular vet check-ups. Originally I wanted a small notebook to keep all the veterinarian notes orderly. I needed easy access, easy record keeping and portability. These folders work great. Each cat has his or her own folder. I stuff each folder with any information I get from the doctor's office. I don 't have to copy endless in formation into separate notebooks. I can quickly grab a folder and I know whose due a vaccine, who needs nail trimming and who gets what pills. These folders will work for keeping many many other pieces of in formation organized.
